data.description: Come and see this affordable cape style home conveniently located in South Hadley ! This home boasts the best of both worlds , while being so close to city amenities you can also enjoy the private oasis in the backyard featuring a large coy pond equipped with an adorable crossing bridge. This 3 bed 2 bath home has undergone several upgrades in recent years, including all new smart appliances, a metal roof, and a partially finished basement . Don’t miss the first showing on Saturday, February 24th, from 11am to 1pm. Bring your ideas and your offers because this home is sure to sell quickly!
